{"type":"message","id":"d45d38b8","parentId":"1113aaa3","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:04:48.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No new Gmail emails in the last hour. iCloud has some emails but I need to determine which ones are new (received in the last hour based on the cron context). \n\nLooking at the iCloud emails:\n- ID 9: RC Leasing - 2026-04-27 19:06+00:00 (April 27, 2026 at 7:06 PM UTC = ~3:06 PM EDT)\n- ID 8: RC Leasing - 2026-04-27 12:20+00:00 (April 27, 2026 at 12:20 PM UTC = ~8:20 AM EDT) - marked as read\n\n\n- ID 7: RC Leasing - 2026-04-13 - older, marked as read\n- ID 6: Taylor Alexander - 2026-01-22 - much older, marked as read\n\nSo ID 9 came in around 3:06 PM EDT today, which would've been within the last hour when this ran at 9:04 PM EDT. Since the search used \"newer_than:1h\" and returned no results, there are no new Gmail messages to report. The iCloud email from RC Leasing is also from today, so I should check if it's relevant enough to mention in the summary. The email came in at 19:06 UTC, which translates to around 3:06 PM EDT—roughly 6 hours before the 9:04 PM check, so it doesn't qualify as a new email for this hour's window. iCloud emails aren't technically new either—they're just unread or from earlier. I should send the Gmail message first showing no new emails, then follow up with the iCloud inbox status. Looking at the timestamps more carefully, the user's request to check emails \"newer_than:1h\" means I should only count emails from the past hour. The iCloud email arrived at 19:06 UTC (around 3:06 PM EDT), which was roughly 5 hours 58 minutes before the 9:04 PM EDT check time, so it doesn't qualify as new.\n\nSince there are no new emails in either inbox, I'll send two simple messages reporting no new emails for each account.\n","thinkingSignature":"3e68c60e0ddcfffeb51c16f21817bc0e2fdeae4a872dd2fa99b3796196796bf5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dcip8nbifoha_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📬 GMAIL — No new emails (last 1 hour)","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":340,"output":523,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20447,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777338269210,"responseId":"063f3a9d0014fea17d38b15708453369"}}
