{"type":"message","id":"421bf138","parentId":"56aff431","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:04:53.275Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me read the iCloud emails to get details, especially the unread one (flag !).\n","thinkingSignature":"9357a674a4845a45563c11c47dada32a968dd354b0f45c00bc93e1754aec89c0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_olvnqj37mqrr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 9 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_olvnqj37mqrr_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":122,"cacheRead":19904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777338289583,"responseId":"063f3ab1f0f0b53e4df118e6d55fd416"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3e7136f3","parentId":"421bf138","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:04:54.599Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_olvnqj37mqrr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY764sNG7nzeTNk205sqlh51LSxHmm3UagO9pU1g7oyg4Nu9RCxMdyC4VubcqUMJe9DZm2xDNEtOuHzb9KCnXKHYAAiSNqZ3EEpb0dBiHtUSqPPUoujDGq19qMXX8SRktVdVh1uYTOkXP7vECkzX-_-Ar_otcb3UI-gg.MEUCIQCrAoq9O9zx8X-WiCWAUINSyTP-_NOMlxkZwbLwiSoYkQIgeBorTOa8cgxlkQb1ARuodw22Fxfr2BJ6_Md9GJYWmkA>\n\n\n\n<Outlook-A picture .png>\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com> <rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1293,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY764sNG7nzeTNk205sqlh51LSxHmm3UagO9pU1g7oyg4Nu9RCxMdyC4VubcqUMJe9DZm2xDNEtOuHzb9KCnXKHYAAiSNqZ3EEpb0dBiHtUSqPPUoujDGq19qMXX8SRktVdVh1uYTOkXP7vECkzX-_-Ar_otcb3UI-gg.MEUCIQCrAoq9O9zx8X-WiCWAUINSyTP-_NOMlxkZwbLwiSoYkQIgeBorTOa8cgxlkQb1ARuodw22Fxfr2BJ6_Md9GJYWmkA>\n\n\n\n<Outlook-A picture .png>\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com> <rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777338294599}}
