{"type":"message","id":"bb68be5c","parentId":"19b46608","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:05:12.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The iCloud emails from RC Leasing are all about the apartment application, and they're all from the last few days. The most recent one (#9) was received at 19:06 UTC today (April 27), which is about 6 hours ago. The cron job is supposed to check \"newer_than:1h\" for Gmail but iCloud doesn't have that filter built in. Looking at the timestamps:\n\n- #9: 2026-04-27 19:06+00:00 (7:06 PM UTC = 3:06 PM ET, about 6 hours ago)\n- #8: 2026-04-27 12:20+00:00 (8:20 AM ET, about 12 hours ago) - has flags \"!\"\n- #7: 2026-04-13 (2 weeks ago)\n- #6: 2026-01-22 (very old)\n\nSo #9 is from today but not within the last hour. Given that this is a cron that runs hourly, I should probably report on emails from today that might be relevant. However, the task says to report \"new\" emails. Since these are from earlier today, let me think about what makes sense.\n\nActually, looking at message #8 marked with \"!\" flag - that might mean flagged/unread. But #9 doesn't have a flag, so it might be read already.\n\nThe task asks for \"new\" emails - these are from today but technically not \"newer_than:1h\". Since Gmail returned no results for the last hour, and iCloud has emails from today, I should probably include them since they're from today and haven't been reported in a while. This is a nightly check (9:04 PM), so these are from earlier today.\n\nLet me report:\n- #9 (RC Leasing, today 7:06 PM UTC) - they may have an apartment for the timeframe\n- #8 (RC Leasing, today 8:20 AM ET) - asking when looking to move by\n\nThese are both apartment-related from RC Leasing. I'll classify as IMPORTANT since they're about the apartment search.\n","thinkingSignature":"0f648a8aa6cb0b4c75f9872051b848a8621c8e98f461223d221b6dedfc8e4d33"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g90l5jrys5gn_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 new today)\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ May have a unit for June timeframe — first come first serve, waiting on Logan to finish application","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1434,"output":539,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777338294602,"responseId":"063f3ab669e69120de464ea06f1887a6"}}
