{"type":"message","id":"1e29f8ed","parentId":"278ce1fc","timestamp":"2026-04-28T01:05:27.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both emails sent. Summary:\n- Gmail: No new emails\n- iCloud: 2 new emails (both from RC Leasing about the apartment - they're the same thread, recent one is urgent/important since it mentions they may have a unit but it's first-come first-serve)\n\nDone.\n","thinkingSignature":"7d3ea49cdee6501edadeaf8b0b14d1d08fc1c599dfbd38b7c7bb61c9c7ceddd5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEmail check complete. Sent both messages back-to-back:\n\n1. **Gmail** — No new emails in the last hour\n2. **iCloud** — 2 new emails, both from RC Leasing about the apartment rental. The most recent one (7:06 PM) is the most important — they may have a unit for your timeframe but it's first-come first-serve. They're waiting on Logan to complete his application portion."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":162,"output":152,"cacheRead":21376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21690,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777338312617,"responseId":"063f3ac85410ced3330c2a8b1f4afac7"}}
